http://www.panda.org:80/thefield/hispanic.htm 204.243.96.56 19970217013352 text/html 10897
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 01:29:44 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 04-Feb-97 14:59:51 GMT
Content-length: 10712
