<TR><TD>95/6</TD><TD> Mixed tropical hardwood</TD><TD> Indonesia </TD><TD>750</TD></TR>

<TR><TD>95/6</TD><TD> Eucalyptus </TD><TD>Chile </TD><TD>32</TD></TR>

