<DOCHDR>
http://www.panda.org:80/research/Africa_Issue/ 204.243.96.56 19970217003225 text/html 2488
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 00:28:20 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 22-Jul-96 20:04:41 GMT
