</td><td width="16%" align=center>



<a href="/siteindx.htm"><font size=2 color="#5c4033">INDEX</font></a>

</td><td width="16%" align=center>



<a href="http://www.panda.org/cgi-bin/mozcheck.pl?NetscapeURL=https://www.newmedium.c om/wwf/join/join.htm&OtherURL=http://www.panda.org/wwf/join/join.htm"><font size=2 color="#5c4033">SUPPORT WWF</font></a>


