http://www.panda.org:80/news/press/news_18.htm 204.243.96.56 19970217022353 text/html 5102
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 02:19:42 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 27-Dec-96 18:27:07 GMT
Content-length: 4919
