<P>
<B>VN0851 Vietnam: Vietnam Environmental Business Council</B><!--VN0851 Vietnam Vietnam Environmental Business Council-->
<BR>
<BR>

<P>
<U><B>Project Summary</B></U><B>:</B>
<P>
This project aims to include environmental considerations into
the massive amounts of private sector international investment
flowing into Vietnam. Follwoing a &quot;Business for Biodiversity&quot;
symposium in late 1995, a Vietnam Environmental Business Council
has been established. This will help guide business investment
to more environmentally sustainable practices by establishing
industrial standards and clarifying and enhancing Vietnam's environmental
legal framework. <BR>

