<P>
<B>RU0024 Russian Federation: Development of a Trust Fund for
Protected Areas in Russia</B><!--RU0024 Russian Federation Development of a Trust Fund for Protected Areas in Russia-->
<BR>
<BR>

<P>
<U><B>Project Summary</B></U><B>:</B>
<P>
The project combines planning of a Trust Fund for protected areas
in Russia with a revision of the current management system of
reserves in the country.<BR>

<TABLE>

<TR><TD WIDTH=307><U><B>Priority Biomes</B></U><B>    <U>%</U></B>
