<B>RU0049 Russian Federation: Baltic Fund for Nature - Organizational
Strengthening, Capacity Building, Training, Information</B><!--RU0049 Russian Federation Baltic Fund for Nature - Organizational Strengthening, Capacity Building, Training, Information-->
<BR>
<BR>

<P>
<U><B>Project Summary</B></U><B>:</B>
<P>
Under this project, WWF-Sweden uses funds received from the Swedish
government to support the development of non&#173;governmental
organizations working on environmental protection and nature conservation
in the Baltic regions of the Russian Federation.<BR>

