<B>9S0050 Asia general: Education Officer Asia/Pacific - Outposted
Staff</B><!--S0050 Asia general Education Officer Asia/Pacific - Outposted Staff-->
<BR>
<BR>

<P>
<U><B>Project Summary</B></U><B>:</B>
<P>
This project aims to facilitate the decentralization of education
and capacity building coordination in the Asia/Pacific region
and to improve interaction with the WWF Asia/Pacific Programme
and with other strategies.<BR>

<TABLE>

<TR><TD WIDTH=307><U><B>Priority Biomes</B></U><B>    <U>%</U></B>
</TD><TD WIDTH=28></TD><TD WIDTH=307><U><B>Strategies</B></U><B>    <U>%</U></B>
</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=307>Forests     20</TD><TD WIDTH=28></TD><TD WIDTH=307>Consumption &amp; Pollution 10
</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=307>Freshwater Ecosystems  20</TD><TD WIDTH=28>
</TD><TD WIDTH=307>EE &amp; Capacity Building  70</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=307>Oceans and Coasts   20</TD><TD WIDTH=28></TD>
<TD WIDTH=307>Protected Areas    10</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=307>Non-Priority Biomes  0</TD><TD WIDTH=28></TD>
<TD WIDTH=307>Species     0</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=307>Non-Biome Specific  40</TD><TD WIDTH=28></TD>
<TD WIDTH=307>Sustainable Resource Use 10</TD></TR>

