<B>(Concept) 9S0039 Asia general: Monitoring the Asian Development
Bank: Policy Case Studies and Advocacy</B><!--S0039 Asia general Monitoring the Asian Development Bank Policy Case Studies and Advocacy-->
<BR>
<BR>

<P>
<U><B>Project Summary</B></U><B>:</B>
<P>
The project will finance case studies of Asian Development Bank
(ADB) activities in the Asia region, to be selected in conjunction
with the Asia Country Teams, and to use the lessons learned in
advocacy with the ADB.
