<P>
<U><B>Project Background:</B></U>
<P>
An important sectoral theme of the SRU strategy is to promote
the reform of the multilateral development institutions, such
as the ADB, which plays a major role, particularly with the private
sector, in development financing in Asia.
<P>
The aim of the project is to analyse on the ground policies and
practices of the ADB so as to monitor, and lobby for, progress
towards sustainable development.<BR>

<P>
<U><B>Project Objectives:</B></U>
<P>
1.  To analyse ADB performance in sustainable development through
local case studies.
<P>
2.  To use the results in advocacy with the ADB.<BR>
<BR>

