<U><I><B>Activity Background:</B></I></U>
<P>
1.  To monitor Multilateral Development Bank policies and projects.
<P>
2.  To lobby in pursuit of objectives.
<P>
3.  To coordinate service on MDB work to local, regional, and
global WWF representation and the MDB network.<BR>
