<P>
<B>(Concept) 9S0075 Asia general: Promoting Ecotourism in Asia</B><!--S0075 Asia general Promoting Ecotourism in Asia-->
<BR>
<BR>

<P>
<U><B>Project Summary</B></U><B>:</B>
<P>
This project aims to promote ecotourism as a means to provide
employment opportunities for local communities, generate income
for protected areas, and achieve conservation at the same time.
More specifically it proposes the establishment of an ecotourism
centre for the Asia region providing the following services: identification
of potential ecotourism sites and assisting local communities
in developing ecotourism programmes; providing information and
advisory services to WWF NOs, POs, field level programmes, other
environmental NGOs, and tourist offices in the region concerned
with ecotourism; developing ecotourism site marketing plans and
specific ecotourism packages for promotion via tour operators,
publishers of travel guides, Internet, press and other media.
<BR>

<TABLE>

<TR><TD WIDTH=307><U><B>Priority Biomes</B></U><B>    <U>%</U></B>
</TD><TD WIDTH=28></TD><TD WIDTH=307><U><B>Strategies</B></U><B>    <U>%</U></B>
</TD></TR>

