<HTML>



<HEAD>



<TITLE>WWF Introductory Guide to the Climate Convention.</TITLE>



<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z Beta">

</HEAD>


<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#0000FF">


<CENTER>

<TABLE CELLPADDING=8 WIDTH=510>

<TD ALIGN=LEFT>




<TABLE CELLPADDING=8 WIDTH=500>

<TR><TD ALIGN=left>


<center><h2><b>3. ANNEXES I and II</b></h2></center>

<hr size=1 noshade>

<tt><b>Joy Hyvarinen, <i>International Treaties Coordinator, January 1996. </i></b></tt>



<p>

<br>

<br>

<tt>Annex I lists industrialized countries and Central

and Eastern European &quot;countries undergoing the process of

transition to a market economy&quot;, all of which have special

commitments under the Convention (see Article 4.2).



<P>

<br>


Annex II lists industrialized countries which are

obliged to provide financial resources and technology to other

countries (see Articles 4.3 and 4.5).

<P>

<br>


Annex II does not include Central and Eastern European

countries.</tt>


<p>

<br>

<br>

<hr size=1 noshade>



<br>



<a href="page1.htm"><tt><b>Back to the previous page</b></tt></a>

</TD></TR>

</TABLE>



</TD>

</TABLE>


</CENTER>


