</TD></TR>



<TR><TD><tt>Yanamarey glacier, Peru</tt><BR>

<BR>

</TD><TD>



<tt>shrinking fast</tt>




</TD><TD>



<tt>ongoing</tt>




</TD></TR>



<TR><TD><tt>Cordillera do M&eacute;rida, Venezuela</tt><BR>

<BR>



