<BR>

</FONT>

</TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=216><FONT FACE="Times"><tt>Raised peat bogs</tt><BR>

<BR>

</FONT>

</TD><TD WIDTH=386><FONT FACE="Times"><tt>Mean summer temperature<BR>

Mean annual precipation</tt><BR>

<BR>

</FONT>

</TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=216><FONT FACE="Times"><tt>Alpine/Mountains</tt><BR>

