<HTML>
<HEAD>

<TITLE>Executive Summary</TITLE>

<!-- Date: Monday, June 10, 1996  11:18 AM -->

</HEAD>
<BODY background="background4.jpg" text="#000000" link="#ff0000" 
vlink="#ffoo66">
<center>
<P>
<P>
<center>
<table border=0 cellpadding=10 width=550><tr><td width=70>
<BR>

</td><td align=left width=460>

<center>
<img src="title.gif" alt="Marine Fishing"><P>
<IMG SRC="shark15.gif" ><BR>

<center>
<font size=-1 font color="#3333ff">
by Elizabeth Kemf, Michael Sutton, and Alison Wilson
</font></center>
<BR>
<BR>
