http://www.panda.org:80/research/country/nepal/page5.htm 204.243.96.56 19970217031650 text/html 7920
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 03:12:40 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 13-Jun-96 21:23:31 GMT
