http://www.panda.org:80/research/country/nepal/page7.htm 204.243.96.56 19970217031719 text/html 3362
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 03:13:08 GMT
