<head>

<title> WWF Finland-Goals/Priority Areas </title>

</head>

<body background="graphics/bg1.gif" link="#ffffff" vlink="#ffffff" alink="#ff0000">

<table  width=85% border=0>

<tr><td width=125 valign=top>
<center>
<img src="graphics/wwflogo4.gif" alt="wwf logo">
</center>
<p>
<br>
<font size=2>
<a href="profile.htm"><b>Profile</b></a><p><a href="goals.htm"><b>Goals/Priority Areas</b></a><p>
<a href="forests.htm"><b>Protection of Forests</b></a><p>
<a href="fresh.htm"><b>Protection of Freshwater Ecosystems</b></a><p>
<a href="landscape.htm"><b>Landscape Management</b></a><p>
<a href="baltic.htm"><b>Protection of the Baltic Sea</b></a><p>
<a href="arctic.htm"><b>Protection of the Arctic Environment</b></a><p>
<a href="wwffinland.htm"><b>WWF-Finland: In the International Arena</b></a><p>
<a href="whatyou.htm"><b>What You Can Do</b></a><p>
</font>
</td>

<td width=30><br>&nbsp;</td>
<td width=465 valign=middle>
<img src="graphics/goalshd2.gif" alt="goals/priority areas">
<p>
<br>
<img src="graphics/goalsimg.jpg" align=right alt="shore of a lake">

<b>WWF-Finlands main objectives are:</b>
<p>
<ul type circle>
<li>Preserving genetic species and ecosystem diversity 
<li> Ensuring that the use of renewable natural resources is sustainable both now and in the long term 
<li>Promoting action to reduce pollution and the wasteful exploitation and consumption of  resources and energy.
</ul>
<p>
<b>Priority Areas</b>
<p>
<ul type circle>
<li>Protection of forests
<li>Protection of freshwater ecosystems 
<li>Landscape management 
<li>Protection of  the Baltic Sea 
<li>Protection of the Arctic environment (especially the Finnish Lapland) 
<p>
<br>

