<head>

<title> WWF Finland-What You Can Do </title>

</head>

<body background="graphics/bg1.gif" link="#ffffff" vlink="#ffffff" alink="#ff0000">

<table  width=85% border=0>

<tr><td width=125 valign=top>
<center>
<img src="graphics/wwflogo4.gif" alt="wwf logo">
</center>
<p>
<br>
<font size=2>
<a href="profile.htm"><b>Profile</b></a><p><a href="goals.htm"><b>Goals/Priority Areas</b></a><p>
<a href="forests.htm"><b>Protection of Forests</b></a><p>
<a href="fresh.htm"><b>Protection of Freshwater Ecosystems</b></a><p>
<a href="landscape.htm"><b>Landscape Management</b></a><p>
<a href="baltic.htm"><b>Protection of the Baltic Sea</b></a><p>
<a href="arctic.htm"><b>Protection of the Arctic Environment</b></a><p>
<a href="wwffinland.htm"><b>WWF-Finland: In the International Arena</b></a><p>
<a href="whatyou.htm"><b>What You Can Do</b></a><p>

</font>
</td>

<td width=30><br>&nbsp;</td> <td width=465 valign=middle> <img src="graphics/whatyouhd2.gif" alt="what you can do"> <p> <br>
<img src="graphics/whatyouimg.jpg" align=right alt="harbor">

It is only with the help of people that WWF can achieve its goals. You can make the vital difference between a dying planet 
and restoration of the earth by contributing to the organization's cause.
<p>
The easiest way to do this is by donations. Every donation counts. In fact, the work of WWF-Finland is made possible by 
contributions from corporations and individuals across the world. If you want to be more closely associated with the work of 
WWF-Finland, you can also join it as a member. 
<p> 
For more information, please contact:  
<p> 
WWF-Finland, <br>
Lintulahdenkatu 10, <br>
00500 Helsinki, <br>
Finland <br>
<p> 
Tel:<b> 09-774 0100</b> <br>
Fax:<b> 09-7740 2139</b> <br>
<p> 
Remember: In nature conservation, all victories are temporary, the losses are final. Help WWF-Finland reduce these losses. 


