<center><h2><b>CAMEROON: VITAL STATISTICS</b></h2></center>

<hr size=1 noshade>

<p>

<br>
Area (km<SUP>2</SUP>)  ...............................................................475,442*
<P>

Population estimate 1994 .........................................13 million**
<P>


Average population density per km<SUP>2</SUP> ..........................26
<P>


Projected population in 2025 .....................................29.26 million
<p>


GNP per capita, in US$ ............................................858
<P>


Protected regions as % of land areas .........................5.1%
<P>

Protected areas (km<SUP>2</SUP>) ...............................................24,380
<P>

Number of protected areas sites .................................19

<P>
<br>
Capital city  Yaound&eacute;

<P>
Languages French, English and over 200 local languages
<P>
Currency CFA Franc

<dl>

<FONT SIZE=2>*Slightly larger than California

<P>

**More than twice the population of Switzerland

</dl>

