<h3>Below are the steps that governments are urged to take.  Fill in the appropriate contact information and the Living Planet Campaign will send you information on the selected action items.
<p>
Please send urgent information on how to:<br>
</h3>

     
<INPUT TYPE=checkbox VALUE="Send me info on" NAME="Establishing networks"> Establish networks of protected areas that help 
ensure conservation of the Global 200 <p>
<INPUT TYPE=checkbox VALUE="Send me info on" NAME="Ratify"> 
Ratify, strengthen, and fulfill theirobligations under treaties such as the UN Climate Convention, the Biodiversity Convention, and the new 
world Fisheries treaty
<p>
<INPUT TYPE=checkbox VALUE="Send me info on" NAME="End subsidies">
End subsidies that encourage over exploitation of fish stocks <p>

<INPUT TYPE=checkbox VALUE="Send me info on" NAME="Adopt policies">
Adopt policies that reduce dependence on coal, oil, and gas <p>

<INPUT TYPE=checkbox VALUE="Send me info on" NAME="End the unsustainable">
End the unsustainable trade in wildlife, and 
take action to save the tiger, the giant panda, and the African black rhino
<p>
<p>
<pre>
Name:     <input TYPE=text NAME="name" MAXLENGTH=40 SIZE=40>
Gov't:    <INPUT TYPE=TEXT NAME="Government Organization" maxlength=10 size=10>      
Address:  <INPUT TYPE=text NAME="addr1" MAXLENGTH=50 SIZE=50>
Address:  <INPUT TYPE=text NAME="addr2" MAXLENGTH=50 SIZE=50>
