http://www.panda.org:80/research/country/vietnam/page10.htm 204.243.96.56 19970217032124 text/html 13844
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 03:17:06 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 29-May-96 21:40:54 GMT
